gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Pelicans 142, Wizards 122
gameRecap.excerpt: The Pelicans defeated the Wizards, 142-122. Brandon Ingram led the way with 40 points, three assists, and two rebounds, with Trey Murphy III adding a season-high 27 points (6-7 3PM) and six rebounds off the bench in the victory. Kyle Kuzma tallied 27 points, seven rebounds, and four assists for the Wizards in the loss. The Pelicans improve to 14-11 in the regular season, while the Wizards fall to 3-20.
